cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with a computer vision problem of novel view synthesis using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for learning and prediction, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves structured prediction problems, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of stereo-vision and camera motion interpretation could be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics), respectively.
